@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 14

title In-Place Pod Vertical Scaling (K8s 1.33 Beta)

skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor<<pod>> #90EE90
  BackgroundColor<<kubelet>> #87CEEB
  BackgroundColor<<api>> #FFB6C1
}

rectangle "Avant: Resize classique" as before {
  rectangle "Pod v1\nCPU: 100m\nMem: 128Mi" as pod1 <<pod>>
  rectangle "Pod v2\nCPU: 200m\nMem: 256Mi" as pod2 <<pod>>
  pod1 -[#red]-> pod2 : **Suppression + Recreation**\n(Downtime)
}

rectangle "Apres: In-Place Resize" as after {
  rectangle "Pod\nCPU: 100m -> 200m\nMem: 128Mi -> 256Mi" as pod3 <<pod>>
  rectangle "kubelet" as kubelet <<kubelet>>
  rectangle "API Server" as api <<api>>

  api -down-> kubelet : PATCH resize subresource
  kubelet -down-> pod3 : Update cgroups\n**Sans redemarrage**
}

note right of after
  **Conditions du Pod:**
  - PodResizePending
  - PodResizeInProgress

  **Avantages:**
  - Zero downtime
  - Pas de rescheduling
  - Connections maintenues
end note

legend right
  |= Methode |= Downtime |= Connections |
  | Classique | Oui | Perdues |
  | **In-Place** | **Non** | **Maintenues** |
endlegend

footer **Cas d'usage:** Scaling vertical automatique, ajustement charge, HPA vertical
@enduml
